<template>
  <n-result status="403" title="503 服务器娘挂了哦" description="要不要听听歌呢">
    <template #footer>
      <n-button type="primary" @click="menuClick" key="E404">找点乐子吧</n-button>
    </template>
  </n-result>
</template>

<script>
import { defineComponent } from "vue";

export default defineComponent({
  setup() {
    function handleClick() {
      window.open("https://res.kcn3388.club/404.html", "_blank");
    }
    return {
      handleClick,
    };
  },
  methods: {
    menuClick(e) {
      // 路由跳转
      this.$router.push(e.key);
    },
  },
});
</script>
